data.description: PRICE REDUCED!  Seller's are willing to credit money to buy down your interest rate and VA assumable loan also available.  Beautiful San Carlos Home in the nicest cul-de-sac neighborhood.  Remodeled kitchen w/ Samsung Smart Home appliances, (3 year warranty on all appliances) quartz countertops, large island w/tons of storage, wood beams & luxury waterproof vinyl floors. New wet bar/den. 1 bed/1 bath on the main level, great for guests/family visiting! Real wood stairs, & the large primary bedrm has 3 closets & bthrm ensuite.   Enjoy the sparkling pool & slide on warm summer days. Cozy up by the fireplace on a cold night. Mtn views, Hike Cowles Mtn, enjoy Lake Murray Park, close to 125, 8 & 52 freeways.
